snippet.textDisplay:
I'm Mexican, so my skin is more medium, but my lips have always looked like I have dark liner around them, my top lip is also a little darker than the bottom lip.
In proportion to my skin tone it is noticeable, and it has always bothered me, I've spent my life feeling jealous of people with pale one toned lips. I hope I can work on liking them how they are.
